---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — AI Tools Nav">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: 32px; max-width: 740px; margin: 40px auto;">
    <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 32px;">Last updated: July 2026</p>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text);">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>AI Tools Nav does not collect personal information beyond standard web analytics. We use minimal cookies for site functionality. Third-party services (Google AdSense, Cloudflare) may collect anonymized data per their privacy policies.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text);">2. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use essential cookies for site security (Cloudflare). We do not use tracking cookies for advertising personalization ourselves. However, Google AdSense, a third-party advertising service, may place cookies on your browser to serve relevant ads and measure ad performance.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text);">3. Google AdSense &amp; Advertising Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google AdSense uses cookies (such as the DoubleClick cookie) and web beacons to serve ads based on your visits to this site and other websites across the internet. These cookies enable Google and its partners to serve personalized ads based on your interests.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 12px;">Data collected by Google AdSense may include:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 4px;">
        <li>Your IP address (truncated for anonymization where possible)</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Pages visited and time spent on the site</li>
        <li>Ad interaction data (clicks, impressions)</li>
        <li>A unique cookie identifier</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text);">4. Your Advertising Choices</h2>
      <p>You can opt out of personalized advertising from Google AdSense by visiting:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 4px;">
        <li><a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a> — manage your ad preferences and opt out of personalized ads from Google.</li>
        <li><a href="https://optout.networkadvertising.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Network Advertising Initiative (NAI) Opt-Out</a> — opt out of interest-based advertising from multiple participating ad networks.</li>
        <li><a href="https://youradchoices.com/control" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YourAdChoices (Digital Advertising Alliance)</a> — control interest-based advertising from participating companies.</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 12px;">Alternatively, you can disable third-party cookies entirely in your browser settings. Please note that opting out of personalized ads does not mean you will stop seeing ads — ads will simply be less relevant to your interests.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text);">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>AI Tools Nav uses the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 4px;">
        <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — advertising (see Section 3 for cookie details)</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — CDN and security</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 8px;">Each service operates under its own privacy policy. We encourage you to review them.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text);">6. GDPR (European Economic Area Users)</h2>
      <p>If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), you have the following data protection rights under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR):</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 4px;">
        <li><strong>Right to Access</strong> — request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Rectification</strong> — request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Erasure</strong> — request deletion of your data where there is no compelling reason to continue processing.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Restrict Processing</strong> — request limited use of your data under certain circumstances.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Data Portability</strong> — request transfer of your data to another service.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Object</strong> — object to processing for direct marketing or legitimate interests.</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 12px;">Our lawful basis for processing data through Google AdSense is your consent. You can withdraw consent at any time via the opt-out links in Section 4. To exercise your GDPR rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@aitoolsnav.net">privacy@aitoolsnav.net</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text);">7. CCPA (California Residents)</h2>
      <p>If you are a resident of California, USA, the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) grants you the following rights:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 4px;">
        <li><strong>Right to Know</strong> — request details about the categories and specific pieces of personal information we have collected about you.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Delete</strong> — request deletion of personal information we have collected from you.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Opt-Out of Sale</strong> — direct us not to "sell" your personal information. Note: AI Tools Nav does not sell personal information. However, the use of third-party advertising cookies may be considered a "sale" under the CCPA's broad definition. You can opt out of this data sharing via the Google Ads Settings link in Section 4.</li>
        <li><strong>Right to Non-Discrimination</strong> — we will not discriminate against you for exercising your CCPA rights.</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 12px;">To exercise your CCPA rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@aitoolsnav.net">privacy@aitoolsnav.net</a>. We will verify your identity and respond within 45 days.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text);">8. Contact</h2>
      <p>Privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:privacy@aitoolsnav.net">privacy@aitoolsnav.net</a></p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
